1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,240
A reviewer clicks Kill Agent and gets a Memory Will receipt with a Walrus blob id.

2
00:00:06,240 --> 00:00:11,520
Private budget notes stay blocked while the successor reads approved memory.

3
00:00:11,520 --> 00:00:16,160
Now write the will to Walrus, then open the cold successor.

4
00:00:16,160 --> 00:00:23,680
Receipt fields show blob id, redactions, replay trace, role, and model output hash.

5
00:00:23,680 --> 00:00:28,320
Inspect Proof reads Walrus plus Sui object fields.

6
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:33,440
In a second browser context, the latest-will path opens the same receipt.
